00:16:40.950 --> 00:16:43.040 align:middle line:90%
other cosmetics giants operated.

00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:46.520 align:middle line:84%
She just thought,
this is ridiculous.

00:16:46.520 --> 00:16:48.820 align:middle line:90%
Women are being--

00:16:48.820 --> 00:16:51.920 align:middle line:84%
I mean she just saw so
many flaws with the system.

00:16:51.920 --> 00:16:53.710 align:middle line:84%
And I think she's a
great classic example

00:16:53.710 --> 00:16:56.890 align:middle line:84%
