00:17:46.810 --> 00:17:48.850 align:middle line:84%
You wouldn't be here
because you wouldn't

00:17:48.850 --> 00:17:52.360 align:middle line:84%
have been able to get on
the plane or in your car.

00:17:52.360 --> 00:17:55.080 align:middle line:84%
Literally, there
would be no lights.

00:17:55.080 --> 00:17:56.770 align:middle line:90%
We would have major problems.

00:17:56.770 --> 00:17:59.320 align:middle line:84%
So our lives would be
drastically different.

00:17:59.320 --> 00:18:02.470 align:middle line:84%
So in every case and
with every industry,

00:18:02.470 --> 00:18:04.900 align:middle line:84%
it is really about
gradual progress.

