00:20:30.920 --> 00:20:31.970 align:middle line:90%
that he struck.

00:20:31.970 --> 00:20:34.370 align:middle line:90%
So he made it a requirement.

00:20:34.370 --> 00:20:37.226 align:middle line:84%
He said, you know, we
have to do it this way,

00:20:37.226 --> 00:20:39.600 align:middle line:84%
and we have to continue because
this is what we are about

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:42.890 align:middle line:84%
