I don't want your money.

00:20:46.290 --> 00:20:47.940 align:middle line:90%
So that was a requirement.

00:20:47.940 --> 00:20:50.080 align:middle line:84%
So they are contractually
obligated to let

00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:54.760 align:middle line:84%
the company continue to
help versus harm society.

00:20:54.760 --> 00:20:56.010 align:middle line:90%
It's really amazing.

00:20:56.010 --> 00:21:00.170 align:middle line:84%
So Stonyfield will continue
to deliver the absolute best

00:21:00.170 --> 00:21:03.310 align:middle line:84%
