00:26:44.040 --> 00:26:47.210 align:middle line:84%
areas of the world
and helping to raise

00:26:47.210 --> 00:26:50.800 align:middle line:84%
the socioeconomic status of
the people who live there.

00:26:50.800 --> 00:26:52.770 align:middle line:84%
So what HP has
