00:30:02.110 --> 00:30:04.540 align:middle line:84%
and touch people from
all over the world,

00:30:04.540 --> 00:30:06.720 align:middle line:84%
the more it's within
their best interest

00:30:06.720 --> 00:30:09.805 align:middle line:84%
to help people from
all over the world.

00:30:09.805 --> 00:30:11.680 align:middle line:84%
So that's why those two
trends are connected.

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:13.170 align:middle line:90%
It's really interesting.

00:30:13.170 --> 00:30:16.760 align:middle line:84%
So for instance, Eziba
