00:30:23.150 --> 00:30:26.260 align:middle line:84%
And all that's needed to
unleash that potential

00:30:26.260 --> 00:30:28.100 align:middle line:90%
is the right environment.

00:30:28.100 --> 00:30:30.860 align:middle line:84%
So that company's
creating the environment,

